Amazon MX Player presents 
Aukaat Ke Bahar - Official Trailer

Genre: Drama Romance
 
About Aukaat Ke Bahar: Rajveer Ahlawat, a small-town boxer from Safidon, enters Delhi‚Äôs elite St. Collins college to fulfill his brother‚Äôs dream of becoming a polished, English-speaking graduate. Amidst bullies, culture shocks, and class divides, he falls for Antara Shukla ‚Äî a senior with political aspirations and far out of his league. When a humiliating dare collides with his growing feelings and a family crisis back home, Rajveer must fight harder than ever ‚Äî this time, not for glory, but for love, dignity, and survival.

About Amazon MX Player
Amazon MX Player is India‚Äôs leading free, premium, ad-supported entertainment service in India. It offers a diverse range of award-winning web series, reality shows, popular international shows, and a massive movie library across multiple genres. With a strong focus on original content, Amazon MX Player has launched some of the largest shows in India, which includes Ek Badnaam Aashram, Campus Diaries, Jamnapaar, Half CA, Bhaukaal, Raktanchal, Dehati Ladke, Who‚Äôs your Gynac, Sixer, Hip Hop India, Hunter ‚Äì Totega Nahi Todega and more. Amazon MX Player also offers a rich selection of international content dubbed in Hindi, Tamil, and Telugu under MX Vdesi, featuring popular shows like What's Wrong With Secretary Kim?, Daydreamer, Gangnam Beauty, My Girlfriend Is An Alien, Put Your Head On My Shoulder, Our Story, and more!

id.title: Aukaat Ke Bahar - Trailer Resmi bersama Elvish Yadav, Nikhil Vijay, Malhaar Rathod | Pemain Amazo...
id.description:
Amazon MX Player mempersembahkan
Aukaat Ke Bahar - Trailer Resmi

Dibintangi: Elvish Yadav, Malhaar Rathod, Nikhil Vijay, Hetal Gada, Rohan Khurrana, Keshav Sadhna
Rumah Produksi: Rusk Studios
Diproduksi Oleh: Rusk Media Pvt. Ltd.
Disutradarai Oleh: Tanmai Rastogi
Dikembangkan, Cerita, Skenario, dan Ditulis oleh: Jayati Pandya, Akhilesh Vats, Jasmeet Bhatia, Ayush Gaur, Sumbul Khan, Siddharth Saini

Genre: Drama Romantis

Tentang Aukaat Ke Bahar: Rajveer Ahlawat, seorang petinju kota kecil dari Safidon, memasuki perguruan tinggi elit St. Collins di Delhi untuk mewujudkan impian saudaranya menjadi lulusan yang cerdas dan berbahasa Inggris. Di tengah perundungan, kejutan budaya, dan perbedaan kelas, ia jatuh cinta pada Antara Shukla ‚Äî seorang mahasiswa tingkat akhir dengan aspirasi politik yang jauh di luar kemampuannya. Ketika sebuah tantangan yang memalukan berbenturan dengan perasaannya yang semakin kuat dan krisis keluarga di kampung halaman, Rajveer harus berjuang lebih keras dari sebelumnya ‚Äî kali ini, bukan demi kejayaan, melainkan demi cinta, martabat, dan kelangsungan hidup.

Tentang Amazon MX Player
Amazon MX Player adalah layanan hiburan gratis, premium, dan beriklan terkemuka di India. Layanan ini menawarkan beragam serial web pemenang penghargaan, acara realitas, acara internasional populer, dan koleksi film yang sangat banyak dari berbagai genre. Dengan fokus yang kuat pada konten orisinal, Amazon MX Player telah meluncurkan beberapa acara terbesar di India, termasuk Ek Badnaam Aashram, Campus Diaries, Jamnapaar, Half CA, Bhaukaal, Raktanchal, Dehati Ladke, Who‚Äôs your Gynac, Sixer, Hip Hop India, Hunter ‚Äì Totega Nahi Todega, dan banyak lagi. Amazon MX Player juga menawarkan beragam pilihan konten internasional yang dialihbahasakan ke dalam bahasa Hindi, Tamil, dan Telugu di bawah naungan MX Vdesi, menampilkan acara-acara populer seperti What's Wrong With Secretary Kim?, Daydreamer, Gangnam Beauty, My Girlfriend Is An Alien, Put Your Head On My Shoulder, Our Story, dan banyak lagi!

Dijadwalkan tayang perdana pada November 2025, musim terakhir ini menjanjikan puncak yang mendebarkan dari saga Hawkins. Setelah penundaan akibat pemogokan industri, produksi selesai pada Desember 2024, dan pascaproduksi berjalan lebih cepat dari jadwal. Duffer Brothers telah menciptakan musim ambisius yang digambarkan sebagai "delapan film blockbuster," dengan fokus pada kedalaman emosi dan aksi berisiko tinggi.

Narasi berpusat pada pertempuran pamungkas kru Hawkins melawan Vecna, menggali lebih dalam misteri Upside Down. Musim ini juga akan mengeksplorasi sifat Upside Down yang menakutkan dan membeku, berpotensi menggabungkan lompatan waktu untuk menyesuaikan dengan para pemain yang menua.

Tambahan baru seperti Linda Hamilton dan Amybeth McNulty bergabung, menambah dinamika segar pada cerita. Delapan judul episode yang telah dikonfirmasi, termasuk "The Crawl," "The Vanishing of‚Ä¶," dan "The Rightside Up," mengisyaratkan musim yang penuh intrik dan petualangan. snippet.description:

Lyricist: Sameer

Song Lyrics:

Aye Hey
La La La La La Ah Ha
La La La La La La Hey
La La La La La La La 
Laa Laa

Aye Meri Natkhati College Ki Ladkiyon Ladkiyon
Yun Mohabbbat Se Mujhko Na Dekha Karo
Meri Chaahat Meri Arzoo Ke Liye
Apni Masoomiyat Ko Na Ruswa Karo
Hai Meri Natkhati College Ki Ladkiyon Ladkiyon
Yun Mohabbbat Se Mujhko Na Dekha Karo

Jo Fisal Jaaye Main Woh Deewana Nahin
Jo Badal Jaaye Main Woh Zamana Nahin
Waar Jaayenge Khali Yeh Tere Sabhi
Teer Nazron Ka Mujh Pe Na Mara Karo
Aye Meri Natkhati College Ki Ladkiyon Ladkiyon
Yun Mohabbat Se Mujhko Na Dekha Karo

Har Kisi Ko Yeh Dildaar Milta Nahin
Itni Aasaani Se Pyaar Milta Nahin
De Raha Hoon Tumhe Mashwara Kaam Ka
Maine Socha Hai Jo Tum Bhi Socha Karo
Aye Meri Natkhati College Ki Ladkiyon Ladkiyon
Yun Mohabbat Se Mujhko Na Dekha Karo

snippet.title: THORATT - SHOOT | OFFICIAL MUSIC VIDEO | PROD. BY FLAMBOY
snippet.description:
Audio Credits :
Written & Performed By - Thoratt 
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/thoratt__/?hl=en
Music Prod  - Flamboy
Mixed & Mastered By - Jason

Video Credits :
Shot By - shotbyshahid
https://www.instagram.com/shotbyshahid_?igsh=MWRtczk5dDZ5bjUycQ==
Edit By - Aeren tunes
https://www.instagram.com/aeren.tunes?igsh=YzJpczl3eW9pb3Zn

Lyrics:
Tu  bas karte rah nakal
Main kar raha hu hustle
Flex nahi karta fir bhi hai nazar
Char dost sath tabhi hoti hai fazar
Tu lavde ka bhai mera koi nahi hai brother
Kapte hai log matlab log jate hadar 
Bad boy sha main change karu weather
Main king street ka king dursa koi nahi idhar
Sunlo koi nahi idhar 

24 saal nikala street pe 
In log se jada mila knowledge streets se
Maine bhi khaye bhot jakham
Par dekha nahi kisi ne pit be 
Teri gand jal jayegi is gane heat dekh 
Thoratt hai stage pe to spin that shit ayee
Fire hai fire hai gana yah lit dekh
Fake log fake call kare fir sim change 
Fans bole diss de kalli ko mal mat pis de
Khabri hai dost tera Ja use tip
Pray Karu do vakt ki roti aur peace de
Kala kar hu zhhaatu bat kar ijjat se 
Karma ko bolu tu bhi karam kar thik se 
khana bat ke khate hum dharam se sike 
Thug life jite par khate nahi chhinke
Kuchal diya ghamand tera kyu ki jute hai
 nike ke

Shot deke bhagte nahi vi kings hai 
Meri dark life bat kare lighting se 
 tight rakhta vers aur tight jeans hai
Clear karu cache bro hygien hai     
Bhugta na tu liya haiye jin se                              
Do do Chahere yah sare twins hai 

Brain wash kare log 
Maherbani rakho mat 
Talk shit kare log 
Toxic bhavde log 
Energy bhari hai 
Moshpit kare show 
Kam kar nar hai to 
Kis pe bhi rahem nahi I feel like a Naruto 
Bolo mat karo to 
Sukoon ki nind jab khuda ghar ho to
Yah hai bambai shehar mout hai dare to

(Hook)
Shoot shoot nakali logo se fasla rahte dur dur 
Madarchod ladke gand fad dalte goons goons 
Gang leke aatu zhatu mujhko dhun dhun 

Brutally bars matlab dhakka dayak 
Daroga ji bole tu to pakka nayak
Pushpa hai nam teri Satta gayab 
Yah mike ko dekhte hi thak ta gayak 
Satte baj ladka bas paise laiye ab 
Tatte bahar chat tu hai chatne layak
Mehanat se naseeb ko ghasit ke laiye ab 
Hood 19 ke kisse kayam

Paap kiye bhot hum nikale bhala karne 
Dost mere bhi sath me the gunha karne
Opps ko jara bhi dete nahi oo aa karne
Lavde Lage to lag jate dua karne 
Gada pap ka toda maine diya nahi bharne 
Ghamand apka toda maine diya chadne
Bandvali badsha bole sula karle

Savdhaan chore mere yade mare gav chan
Ladke log lete supari ai chi Gand yech nav saang
Dikhava karo mat kabhi to bhuke ko khila ke aav jaav
Land khandan mushkil khada tu tere liye jan dan
Koi kisi ka saga nahi aisa koi Mila nahi diya jo nahi daga bat man 

(Hook)
Shoot shoot nakali logo se fasla rahte dur dur 
Madarchod ladke gand fad dalte goons goons 
Gang leke aatu zhatu mujhko dhun dhun

snippet.title: Meri Kismat Mein Tu Nahin Shayad Lyrical | Lata Mangeshkar | Suresh Wadkar | Prem Rog | Rishi Kapoor
snippet.description:
Relive the magic of classic Bollywood with the soulful duet ‚ÄúMeri Kismat Mein Tu Nahin Shayad‚Äù sung by the legendary Lata Mangeshkar and Suresh Wadkar. Featured in the iconic movie Prem Rog starring Rishi Kapoor, this lyrical video brings out the emotion, romance, and timeless charm of old Hindi melodies. üé∂‚ù§Ô∏è

Don‚Äôt forget to like, share for more musical journeys through Bollywood‚Äôs golden era. üëâ Subscribe to Our channel:  https://youtube.com/@SureshWadkarOldSongs-m5c?si=NbrZmfXqKqNRco1a 

Song Credits:
Song: Meri Kismat Mein Tu Nahin Shayad
Artist: Lata Mangeshkar, Suresh Wadkar
Music: Laxmikant-Pyarelal
Lyrics: Amir Qazalbash

Film Credits:
Film: Prem Rog
Director: Raj Kapoor
Producer: Randhir Kapoor
Star Cast: Rishi Kapoor, Padmini Kolhapure, Shammi Kapoor, Nanda, Tanuja, Kulbhushan Kharbanda, Om Prakash, Bindu, Vijayendra, Kiran Vairale, Raza Murad

 Meri Kismat Mein Tu Nahin Shayad Song Lyrics 
meree kismat me too nahee shaayad, kyon teraa intjaar karata hoo
mai tujhe kal bhee pyaar karata tha, mai tujhe abb bhee pyaar karata hoo
aaj samajee hoo pyaar ko shaayad, aaj mai tujhako pyaar karatee hoo
kal meraa intjaar tha tujhako, aaj mai intjaar karatee hoo

sochata hoo ke meree aankho ne, kyon sajaaye the pyaar ke sapne
tujhase maangee thee ek khushee maine, tune gham bhee nahee diye apane
jindagee bojh ban gayee abb toh, abb toh jita hoo aur naa marata hoo
mai tujhe kal bhee pyaar karata tha, mai tujhe abb bhee pyaar karata hoo

abb naa tute yeh pyaar ke rishte, abb yeh rishte sanbhaalane honge
meree raaho se tujhako kal kee tarah, dukh ke kaante nikaalane honge
mil naa jaye khushee ke raste me, gam kee parchhayeeyo se daratee hoo
kal meraa intjaar tha tujhako, aaj mai intjaar karatee hoo

dil nahee ikhtiyaar me mere, jaan jaayegee pyaar me tere
tujhase milane kee aas hain aa jaa, meree duniya uadas hain aa jaa
pyaar shaayad isiko kahate hai, har ghadee bekaraar rahata hoo
raat din teree yaad aatee hai, raat din intjaar karatee hoo
